    - Sync with upstream FHS-compliant paths

 -- Robert E. Lee <robert@unicornscan.org>  Fri, 16 Jan 2026 07:00:00 +0000

unicornscan (0.4.42-0kali1) kali-dev; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release 0.4.42 (35 version jump from 0.4.7)
  * Major new features:
    - Alicorn Web UI: React-based scan result visualization
    - ASN/CIDR hierarchical grouping in network topology view
    - Multi-scan comparison with JSON/CSV/Markdown diff exports
    - Compound scan modes (-mA+T, -mA+U) for ARP-filtered scanning
    - MAC address capture for local network targets
    - GeoIP API service for live IP lookups (DB-IP Lite)
    - PostgreSQL cloud support via PostgREST REST API
  * Added Docker services for Alicorn stack:
    - alicorn-postgres: PostgreSQL 16 for scan data
    - alicorn-postgrest: REST API to database
    - alicorn-geoip: GeoIP lookup service
    - alicorn-web: Nginx serving React frontend
  * Added management scripts:
    - unicornscan-alicorn: Docker container management
    - unicornscan-geoip-update: Download DB-IP Lite databases
  * Updated build dependencies:
    - Added autoconf, automake, libtool for autoreconf
    - Added libpq-dev for PostgreSQL support
    - Added libmaxminddb-dev for GeoIP support
  * Added Docker as hard dependency for full Alicorn experience
  * Updated homepage to unicornscan.org (redirects to GitHub)
  * Post-install sets Linux capabilities for non-root operation

 -- Robert E. Lee <robert@unicornscan.org>  Thu, 16 Jan 2026 04:00:00 +0000

